NAIROBI, KENYA: Tanzanian billionaire Mohammed Dewji has been rescued from kidnappers in early Thursday morning incident which spread like a bush-fire on social media platforms. A local daily in Tanzania says, Dewji was kidnapped on his way to the Oysterbay for routine gym exercise. ALSO READ:

